# returning HANDLER FUNCTION `runSingleCmd : Parsed
# -> IO UInt32`.  Distinct from R322 JCommander
# `@Parameter` (annotation-based), R311 Guile
# `(args:make-option (h help) #:none ... BODY)`
# (embedded body thunk).  Lean 4 Cli's approach:
