# Critical extraction note: doc-gen4 uses **Lean 4
# Cli `Parsed`-object-method-accessor CLI pattern**
# at Main.lean:8-13 et seq — `(p : Parsed) : IO
# UInt32` handler signature; `p.flag? "build"`
# returns `Option Flag` (None if not passed,
# Some flag if passed); `p.flag! "build"` raises
# if not passed; `p.positionalArg! "module" |>.as!
# String` chained access for required positionals;
# `p.variableArgsAs! String` for variadics
# returning `Array String`.  Distinct from R322
# JCommander reflection-based binding, R311 Guile
# `(option-ref options 'build "default")` (alist
# accessor with default), R313 Idris 2 `let (MkResult
# opts [] [] []) = getOpt ...` (pattern-match
