# refs), R313 Idris 2 `getOpt POLICY DESCS ARGS`
# (returns MkResult).  Lean 4 Cli's approach:
# SINGLE METHOD CALL on the root Cmd that does
# everything — corpus's **first documented
# validate-method-on-Cmd CLI parser pattern**.
